{
  "description": "A long, modern bridge spans a wide body of water under a clear blue sky with wispy clouds. The bridge consists of a main suspension section with tall white pylons connected by cables, and a lower parallel bridge section built on concrete pillars. A small flock of birds flies above the suspension bridge. In the foreground, there is water and a portion of a concrete pier with a small building on it, and a few boats near the shoreline.  The distant shoreline is visible, with subtle green vegetation. The lighting suggests either early morning or late afternoon.",
